<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <title>{% block title %}MeetOUT - Home{% endblock %}</title>
        {% block stylesheets %}
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/style.css') }}"/>
            <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ asset('css/hover-min.css') }}"/>
            <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto" rel="stylesheet">
            <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat" rel="stylesheet">
        {% endblock %}
        <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="{{ asset('favicon.ico') }}" />
    </head>
    <body class="homepage">

        {% block body %}

            <header class="home-head">
                {% block header %}
                    <ul class="header-home">
                        <li><a href="#"><img src="{{ asset('img/logo.png') }}" alt="MeetOut logo"/></a></li>
                        <li>
                            <div class="modal">
                                <input id="modal__trigger" type="checkbox" />
                                <label for="modal__trigger">Iniciar sesión</label>
                                <div class="modal__overlay" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="modal__title" aria-describedby="modal_desc">
                                    <div class="modal__wrap">
                                        <label for="modal__trigger">&#10006;</label>
                                        <h2 id="modal__title">Inicia sesión</h2>
                                        <div id="modal__desc">
                                            <h1>FORMULARIO LOGIN</h1>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                {% endblock %}
            </header>

            <div class="content">
                <section id="hizq">
                    <span>
                        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aenean fringilla, libero at ornare sodales, tellus turpis faucibus purus, eu suscipit nisl quam a felis. Cras blandit tempus purus vitae facilisis.
                        Duis dignissim quam vel dictum pretium. Aenean metus dui, tincidunt et quam nec, aliquam feugiat ligula. <br/><br/>Quisque eget dui malesuada, scelerisque augue eu, maximus arcu. Sed a velit nec justo molestie consectetur. Quisque sit amet mauris auctor, vulputate elit a, condimentum turpis. Pellentesque auctor consectetur fringilla. Pellentesque sit amet dui gravida, viverra felis nec, consectetur nibh. Donec sodales tortor libero, porttitor maximus eros pellentesque sed. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Mauris eleifend venenatis dui eget gravida. Ut metus ex, suscipit at ante sed, maximus elementum dui.
                        Cras quis felis vel sem tristique dignissim. Sed sit amet luctus nisi.
                    </span>
                </section>



                <section id="hder">
                    <div class="wrapper-hder">
                        <div class="titleder"><h2 style="color:white;">Eres nuevo? Regístrate!</h2></div>
                        <div id="wrapper-form">
                            {% spaceless %}
                            {{ form_start(form_registry) }}
                            {{ form_widget(form_registry) }}
                                <div>
                                    <a href="register" ><input type="button"  value="¡Registrate!" /></a>
                                </div>
                            {{ form_end(form_registry) }}
                            {% endspaceless %}
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </section>
            </div>

            {% include '/extends/footer.html.twig' %}

        {% endblock %}
    </body>
</html>
